    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the Chinese-style braised beef has had 30-35 min, reboil half a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>white</strong> <strong>long grain rice </strong>to<strong> </strong>an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>with 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cover tightly with<strong> tin foil </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 25-30 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p>",
