    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the Chinese-style braised beef is ready, remove the dish from the oven</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped Tenderstem broccoli</strong> to the dish with your <strong>tamari soy sauce</strong>, <strong>ginger paste</strong> and <strong>hoisin sauce</strong></p><p>Stir it all together and return the dish to the oven, uncovered, for 12-15 min or until the broccoli is tender and the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>Chinese-style braised beef & broccoli</strong></p>",
